    "title": "Hiring Category Manager at Amazon India",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Amazon India. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Category Manager to strengthen our Jodhpur-based team.\n\nAbout Amazon India:\nAmazon India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Affiliate Marketing\n• Proficiency in Magento\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Flexible working hours\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jodhpur, Rajasthan, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Amazon India!",
